#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Azure Functions with Quarkus REST, Undertow, or Reactive Routes"
msgstr "使用 Quarkus REST、Undertow 或 Reactive Routes 的 Azure Functions"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "<a class=\"status-label status-preview\" title=\"This extension's backward compatibility and presence in the ecosystem is not guaranteed\" href=\"#extension-status-note\">preview</a>"
msgstr "<a class=\"status-label status-preview\" title=\"无法保证此扩展程序的向后兼容性及其在生态系统中的可用性\" href=\"#extension-status-note\">预览</a>"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `quarkus-azure-functions-http` extension allows you to write microservices with Quarkus REST (our Jakarta REST implementation),\n"
"Undertow (servlet), Reactive Routes, or xref:funqy-http.adoc[Funqy HTTP] and make these microservices deployable to the Azure Functions runtime.\n"
"In other words, this extension is a bridge from the Azure Functions HttpTrigger and the Quarkus family\n"
"of HTTP APIs.\n"
"One azure function deployment can represent any number of Jakarta REST, servlet, Reactive Routes, or xref:funqy-http.adoc[Funqy HTTP] endpoints."
msgstr "`quarkus-azure-functions-http` 扩展允许您使用 Quarkus REST（我们的 Jakarta REST 实现）、Undertow（Servlet）、Reactive Routes 或 xref:funqy-http.adoc[Funqy HTTP] 编写微服务，并使这些微服务能够部署到 Azure Functions 运行时。 换言之，该扩展充当了 Azure Functions HttpTrigger 与 Quarkus 系列 HTTP API 之间的桥梁。一个 Azure Functions 部署可以代表任意数量的 Jakarta REST、Servlet、Reactive Routes 或 xref:funqy-http.adoc[Funqy HTTP] 端点。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Only text based media types are supported at the moment as Azure Functions HTTP Trigger for Java does not support a binary format"
msgstr "目前仅支持基于文本的媒体类型，因为 Azure Functions 的 Java HTTP 触发器不支持二进制格式"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "先决条件"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://azure.microsoft.com[An Azure Account].  Free accounts work."
msgstr "link:https://azure.microsoft.com[一个 Azure 账户] 。免费账户即可。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-functions/functions-run-local#v2[Azure Functions Core Tools] version 4.x"
msgstr "link:https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-functions/functions-run-local#v2[Azure Functions Core Tools] 4.x 版"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cli/azure/install-azure-cli[Azure CLI Installed]"
msgstr "link:https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cli/azure/install-azure-cli[已安装 Azure CLI]"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Solution"
msgstr "解决方案"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This guide walks you through running a maven project that can deploy a Quarkus REST endpoint to Azure Functions.\n"
"While only Jakarta REST is provided as an example, you can easily replace it with the HTTP framework of your choice."
msgstr "本指南将引导您运行一个 Maven 项目，该项目可将 Quarkus REST 端点部署到 Azure Functions。虽然这里仅以 Jakarta REST 作为示例，但您可以轻松地将其替换为您选择的 HTTP 框架。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Creating the Maven/Gradle Project"
msgstr "创建 Maven/Gradle 项目"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "First, we need a new project. Create a new project with the following command:"
msgstr "首先，我们需要一个新项目。使用以下命令创建一个新项目："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This command generates a project structure importing the Quarkus Azure Functions HTTP extension.\n"
"It includes an example."
msgstr "该命令会生成一个项目结构，其中导入了 Quarkus Azure Functions HTTP 扩展。该项目包含一个示例。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Examining the project"
msgstr "项目审查"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you open the `pom.xml` or `build.gradle` build file of the generated project you'll see that\n"
"the project is similar to any other Quarkus project.\n"
"The `quarkus-azure-functions-http` extension is the integration point between\n"
"Quarkus and Azure Functions."
msgstr "如果你打开生成的项目的 `pom.xml` 或 `build.gradle` 构建文件，你会发现该项目与其他任何 Quarkus 项目类似。 `quarkus-azure-functions-http` 扩展是 Quarkus 与 Azure Functions 之间的集成点。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The current implementation of the `quarkus-azure-functions-http` extension no longer requires the\n"
"`azure-functions-maven-plugin` or Gradle equivalent.  Local development and Azure Functions packaging and\n"
"deployment is now all done by Quarkus."
msgstr "`quarkus-azure-functions-http` 扩展的当前实现已不再需要 `azure-functions-maven-plugin` 或 Gradle 的等效插件。本地开发以及 Azure Functions 的打包和部署现均由 Quarkus 完成。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Build configuration is all within `application.properties`. The only required configuration switch\n"
"is `quarkus.azure-functions.app-name`."
msgstr "构建配置均位于 `application.properties` 文件中。唯一必需的配置选项是 `quarkus.azure-functions.app-name` 。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Azure Deployment Descriptors"
msgstr "Azure 部署描述符"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The Azure Functions `host.json` deployment descriptor is automatically\n"
"generated, but if you need to override it, declare it in the root directory of the project and\n"
"rerun the build when you are ready."
msgstr "Azure Functions 的 `host.json` 部署描述符是自动生成的，但如果您需要覆盖它，请在项目的根目录中声明该文件，并在准备就绪后重新运行构建。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Configuring Root Paths"
msgstr "配置根路径"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The default route prefix for an Azure Function is `/api`.  All of your Jakarta REST, Servlet, Reactive Routes, and xref:funqy-http.adoc[Funqy HTTP] endpoints must\n"
"explicitly take this into account.  In the generated project, this is handled by the\n"
"`quarkus.http.root-path` switch in `application.properties`"
msgstr "Azure Function 的默认路由前缀为 `/api` 。您所有的 Jakarta REST、Servlet、Reactive Routes 和 xref:funqy-http.adoc[Funqy HTTP] 端点都必须明确考虑这一点。在生成的项目中，这通过 `application.properties` 文件中的 `quarkus.http.root-path` 开关来处理。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus dev mode"
msgstr "Quarkus 开发模式"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus dev mode works by just running your application as an HTTP endpoint.  In dev mode,\n"
"there is no special interaction with the Azure Functions local runtime."
msgstr "Quarkus 的开发模式仅通过将应用程序作为 HTTP 端点运行来实现。在开发模式下，不会与 Azure Functions 本地运行时进行任何特殊交互。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Run locally in Azure Functions local environment"
msgstr "在 Azure Functions 本地环境中运行"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you want to try this example within the local Azure Functions environment, you can\n"
"use this command:"
msgstr "如果您想在本地 Azure Functions 环境中尝试此示例，可以使用以下命令："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Gradle is a bit quirky with process management, so you need the `--no-daemon` switch or control-c will not\n"
"destroy the process cleanly and you'll have open ports."
msgstr "Gradle 在进程管理方面有些特殊，因此你需要使用 `--no-daemon` 参数，否则按下 Ctrl+C 无法干净地终止进程，导致端口保持打开状态。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You must have the https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-functions/functions-run-local#v2[Azure Functions Core Tools]\n"
"installed for this to work."
msgstr "要使此功能正常工作，您必须已安装 link:https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-functions/functions-run-local#v2[Azure Functions Core Tools] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The URL to access the example would be:"
msgstr "访问该示例的 URL 如下："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "http://localhost:8081/api/hello"
msgstr "http://localhost:8081/api/hello"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus Integration Testing"
msgstr "Quarkus 集成测试"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can implement integration tests using `@QuarkusIntegrationTest` functionality.  When these\n"
"integration tests run, the local Azure Functions environment will be spun up for the duration of integration testing."
msgstr "您可以使用 `@QuarkusIntegrationTest` 功能来实现集成测试。当这些集成测试运行时，系统会在集成测试期间启动本地 Azure Functions 环境。"

#. type: Block title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Maven"
msgstr "Maven"

#. type: Block title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Gradle"
msgstr "Gradle"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Make sure any integration tests you execute with Maven use the `*IT.java` file pattern so that regular builds do not execute\n"
"the test."
msgstr "请确保使用 Maven 执行的任何集成测试都采用 `*IT.java` 的文件命名模式，以免常规构建过程中执行该测试。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Make sure any integration tests you execute with Gradle are located within `src/integrationTest/java`. Integration\n"
"tests that exist in `src/test` will run with normal build and fail."
msgstr "请确保使用 Gradle 执行的任何集成测试都位于 `src/integrationTest/java` 目录下。位于 `src/test` 目录下的集成测试会在常规构建过程中运行，并导致构建失败。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Login to Azure"
msgstr "登录 Azure"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To be able to deploy your application to Azure, log in to Azure:"
msgstr "要将应用程序部署到 Azure，请登录 Azure："

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Deploy to Azure"
msgstr "部署到 Azure"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `quarkus-azure-functions-http` extension handles all the work to deploy to Azure. By default,\n"
"Quarkus will use the Azure CLI in the background to authenticate and deploy to Azure. If you have\n"
"multiple subscriptions associated with your account, you must set the `quarkus.azure-functions.subscription-id`\n"
"property in your `application.properties` file to the subscription you want to use.\n"
"For other authentication mechanisms and deployment options, see <<#configuration-reference>>."
msgstr "`quarkus-azure-functions-http` 扩展负责处理所有部署到 Azure 的工作。默认情况下，Quarkus 会在后台使用 Azure CLI 进行身份验证并部署到 Azure。 如果您的账户关联了多个订阅，则必须在 `application.properties` 文件中将 `quarkus.azure-functions.subscription-id` 属性设置为您要使用的订阅。有关其他身份验证机制和部署选项，请参阅 <<configuration-reference>> 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To deploy your application, after you built your project, execute:"
msgstr "要部署您的应用程序，请在构建项目后执行以下命令："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For Gradle, you must use the `--info` switch to see this output."
msgstr "对于 Gradle，必须使用 `--info` 选项才能看到此输出。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If deployment is a success, Quarkus will output the endpoint URL of the example function to the console:"
msgstr "如果部署成功，Quarkus 会将示例函数的端点 URL 输出到控制台："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/azure-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The URL to access the service would be something like: `https://{appName}.azurewebsites.net/api/hello`."
msgstr "访问该服务的 URL 通常类似于： `https://{appName}.azurewebsites.net/api/hello` 。"

